arts.ttl: Sudan seal Afcon 2025 spot as Benin also go through
arts.sum: Sudan's footballers defy their country's civil war to clinch a remarkable qualification for the 2025 Africa Cup of Nations, with Benin also progressing.

arts.ttl: Preview: Sudan vs. Angola - prediction, team news, lineups
arts.sum: Sports Mole previews Monday's Africa Cup of Nations Qualifying clash between Sudan and Angola, including predictions, team news and possible lineups.
